Mods Added:

"Wasteland" Separator. 
This is only to be used in the Wasteland Profile!
I added the Wasteland and a few of the default maps.
Optional Add-on mod you can manually include on your own:
https://7daystodiemods.com/non-script-radios-video-games/
Play Fallout music in your game from a radio. 

"Jen Model Revival" QoL, enabled.
Brings the A19-V2.4 Jen back to 2.5+. 
For those of us who prefer her former appearance.

"Party Scout" Experimental, disabled.
Let's any player's map discovery show on all teammates maps. 
All players effect one another's map fog of war. 
I have not had an oppurtunity to test this. 

"LittleRedSonja Sonja's Vanity Vault" Decor, enabled.
Adds new custom hairs and face paints that you can choose directly in the character creation UI, so they can be used together with any armor.
She's just too good to this community. :P

